      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. i'll try that. it just felt so much more intense than a normal headache though, like i actually felt a bit nauseous for a second too. but yeah, i probably just need the water. do u think i should take any ibuprofen or something now to make sure it doesn't come back? or will that mess with the hydration thing?",
